\cb2 Clo . Sporus is vanquished . Lydon is the conqueror . [ Three shouts . ] Bear hence the body . [ Slow music . -GUARDS take body off , L. , and return . ] Bravely done , young gladiator ! another trial , and the prize is fairly won . Niger , stand forth ! [ Drum and trumpet .\cb1 \
