\cb2 Lydon . Another ? Ye gods ! ye made these men , and these soft smil- ing things , called women , who feast their eyes on blood ! ' Tis for my father's freedom that I fight .\cb1 \
\cb2 Niger . One of us this night must sup with Pluto .\cb1 \
\cb2 Lydon . The will of Jove be done !\cb1 \
